plot: Nolan interrogates a suspected Votanis Collective spy in order to prevent a catastrophic terrorist attack on New York.

Having learned Irina's secret, Nolan makes it clear that there are to be no more secrets and that they will live or die together. Nolan and the military arrest a Votan spy, Mahsuvus Gorarth, who they believe has information about a bomb - a dirty nuke - placed somewhere in New York City. Enhanced interrogation techniques aren't having the desired effect. Amanda meanwhile receives a cryptic phone call telling her to to deliver Mahsuvus to them alive or her sister Kenya will die. Irisa meets her victims who begin to gather in the same place.—garykmcd
